<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQs - Bank Statement Analyser</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/report.css">
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>

        <div class="container py-5">

            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h1 class="report-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                <p class="report-subtitle">
                    Everything you need to know about the Bank Statement Analyser
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">

                <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                            What does this application do?
                        </button>
                    </h2>

                    <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">

                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            This application analyzes bank statements and provides
                            financial insights like income vs expenses,
                            spending categories, recurring payments,
                            unusual transactions, and AI-generated summaries.
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#faq2">

                            Which file formats are supported?

                        </button>
                    </h2>

                    <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">

                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Currently, PDF and CSV bank statements are supported.
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#faq3">

                            Is my data secure?

                        </button>
                    </h2>

                    <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">

                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Yes. Uploaded files are processed temporarily and
                            deleted after analysis. No financial data is stored permanently.
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#faq4">

                            How are transactions categorized?

                        </button>
                    </h2>

                    <div id="faq4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">

                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Transactions are categorized automatically using
                            keyword-based classification rules for food,
                            shopping, travel, subscriptions, utilities, and more.
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#faq5">

                            What AI model powers the summaries?

                        </button>
                    </h2>

                    <div id="faq5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">

                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            The application uses Google's Gemini AI model
                            to generate concise financial insights and recommendations.
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item mb-3">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#faq6">

                            Can the system detect unusual transactions?

                        </button>
                    </h2>

                    <div id="faq6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">

                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Yes. Transactions significantly higher than
                            average spending are highlighted as unusual transactions.
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

            <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
                integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI"
                crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>